===拜耳－维立格氧化反应===
[[File:Baeyer-Villiger_Oxidation.png|400px]]]]
由于其相对于类似的过氧酸和[[过氧化物|过氧化物]]的高酸性，三氟过氧乙酸是拜耳－维立格氧化反应中最强的试剂之一。<ref name = Myers>{{cite web|last = Myers|first = Andrew G.|title = Chemistry 115 Handouts: Oxidation|url = http://faculty.chemistry.harvard.edu/files/myers/files/6-oxidation.pdf|access-date = 10 January 2017|publisher = [[Harvard_University|Harvard University]]|archive-date = 2017-05-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170516231633/http://faculty.chemistry.harvard.edu/files/myers/files/6-oxidation.pdf}}</ref>{{rp|17}}这个反应以于1899年报告此反应的[[阿道夫·冯·拜尔|阿道夫·冯·拜尔]]和{{le|维克多·维立格|Victor Villiger}}命名，可以把[[酮|酮]]氧化成[[酯|酯]]或[[内酯|内酯]]。<ref name = BVoxidation>{{cite book|last1 = Kürti|first1 = László|last2 = Czakó|first2 = Barbara|title = Strategic Applications of Named Reactions in Organic Synthesis|year = 2005|publisher = [[Elsevier|Elsevier Academic Press]]|isbn = 9780124297852|page = 28}}</ref>该反应被认为是通过[[克里格中间体|克里格中间体]]进行的，<ref name = eEROS2012 />并且显示出对氧原子插入位置的良好[[区域选择性|区域选择性]]和{{le|化学选择性|Chemoselectivity}}，以及在相邻位置保留[[立体化学|立体化学]]结构。为了防止强酸性的三氟乙酸副产物造成酯产物的[[水解|水解]]<ref>{{cite book|pages = 259–280|chapter = 6.3 Oxidation of Olefins|chapter-url = https://books.google.com/books?id=xAc4AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA266|title = Some Modern Methods of Organic Synthesis|first = William|last = Carruthers|year = 1971|publisher = [[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]]|isbn = 9780521096430|access-date = 2021-12-30|archive-date = 2021-12-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211230095039/https://books.google.com/books?id=xAc4AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA266}}</ref>和[[酯交换反应|酯交换反应]]<ref>{{cite book|pages = 287–290|chapter = 6.5 Baeyer–Villiger oxidation of ketones|chapter-url = https://books.google.com/books?id=xAc4AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA287|title = Some Modern Methods of Organic Synthesis|first = William|last = Carruthers|year = 1971|publisher = [[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]]|isbn = 9780521096430|access-date = 2021-12-30|archive-date = 2022-04-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220425143004/https://books.google.com/books?id=xAc4AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA287}}</ref>，会加入缓冲物质[[磷酸一氢钠|磷酸一氢钠]] {{chem|Na|2|H|P|O|4}}。<ref name = Hiyama /> 

