===环氧化===
[[Prilezhaev反应|Prilezhaev反应]]是用过氧酸把[[烯烃|烯烃]]氧化成[[环氧化物|环氧化物]]的反应，<ref name = PrilezhaevRxn>{{cite book|chapter = Prilezhaev reaction|pages = 274–281|last = Hagen|first = Timothy J.|chapter-url = https://books.google.com/books?id=WZ0DxnPNAdAC&pg=PA274|title = Name Reactions of Functional Group Transformations|editor1-first = Jie Jack|editor1-last = Li|editor2-first = E. J.|editor2-last = Corey|publisher = [[John_Wiley_&_Sons|John Wiley & Sons]]|year = 2007|isbn = 9780470176504}}</ref>该反应于1909年首次报告。<ref>{{cite journal|first = Nikolaus|last = Prileschajew|year = 1909|title = Oxydation ungesättigter Verbindungen mittels organischer Superoxyde|journal = [[Ber._Dtsch._Chem._Ges.|Ber. Dtsch. Chem. Ges.]]|volume = 42|issue = 4|pages = 4811–4815|doi = 10.1002/cber.190904204100|language = de|trans-title = Oxidation of unsaturated compounds by means of organic superoxides|url = https://zenodo.org/record/1426367|access-date = 2021-12-31|archive-date = 2019-10-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191003023256/https://zenodo.org/record/1426367}}</ref>这个反应是合成[[莨菪烷类生物碱|莨菪烷类生物碱]]{{le|莨菪品碱|scopine}}的最后一步。在这种方法中，由[[九羰基二铁|九羰基二铁]]介导的[4+3] [[环加成反应|环加成反应]]用于构建双环骨架，然后用[[二异丁基氢化铝|二异丁基氢化铝]][[非对映选择性|非对映选择性]]还原酮来引入羟基[[官能团|官能团]]，最后用三氟过氧乙酸的Prilezhaev反应环氧化，完成莨菪品碱的合成。<ref>{{cite journal|last1 = Hayakawa|first1 = Y.|last2 = Baba|first2 = Y.|last3 = Makino|first3 = S.|last4 = Noyori|first4 = R.|journal = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]|year = 1978|volume = 100|pages = 1786–1791|issue = 6|title = Carbon-carbon bond formation promoted by transition metal carbonyls. 19. General synthesis of tropane alkaloids via the polybromo ketone-iron carbonyl reaction|doi = 10.1021/ja00474a021}}</ref>

