===重排氧化===
三氟过氧乙酸和[[三氟化硼|三氟化硼]]一起使用，对烯烃和[[芳香环|芳香环]]的氧化反应就伴随着分子骨架的[[重排反应|重排反应]]。<ref name = eEROS2012 />

对于烯烃，它的氧化产物是酮，不过反应机理不是简单的环氧化后发生BF<sub>3</sub>催化的[[瓦格纳－梅尔外因重排反应|瓦格纳－梅尔外因重排反应]]：<ref>{{cite journal|title = Oxidations with peroxytrifluoroacetic acid-boron trifluoride. IX. Direct oxidation of alkenes to ketones using peroxytrifluoroacetic acid–boron fluoride|first1 = Harold|last1 = Hart|first2 = Lawrence R.|last2 = Lerner|journal = [[J._Org._Chem.|J. Org. Chem.]]|year = 1967|volume = 32|issue = 9|pages = 2669–2673|doi = 10.1021/jo01284a004}}</ref>

[[File:Alkene_TFPAA-BF3.png|frameless]]

