===芳香环的氧化断裂===
除了把芳香环氧化成羰基化合物（见[[#重排氧化|重排氧化章节]]）以外，三氟过氧乙酸还能使芳香环的碳-碳键完全[[键结断裂|断裂]]。在{{le|烷基芳香烃|alkylaromatic}}的氧化反应中，其它氧化剂会断裂烷基部分并产生苯甲酸和相关化合物，而三氟过氧乙酸则会留下烷基并断裂芳香环。<ref name=Deno1978>{{cite journal|title = New method for elucidating the structures of coal|first1 = Norman C.|last1 = Deno|first2 = Barbara A.|last2 = Greigger|first3 = Stephen G.|last3 = Stroud|journal = Fuel|volume = 57|issue = 8|year = 1978|pages = 455–459|doi = 10.1016/0016-2361(78)90153-9}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title = Aromatic ring oxidation of alkylbenzenes|first1 = Norman C.|last1 = Deno|first2 = Barbara A.|last2 = Greigger|first3 = Lauren A.|last3 = Messer|first4 = Michael D.|last4 = Meyer|first5 = Stephen G.|last5 = Stroud|journal = [[Tetrahedron_Lett.|Tetrahedron Lett.]]|volume = 18|issue = 20|year = 1977|pages = 1703–1704|doi = 10.1016/S0040-4039(01)93253-8}}</ref>

[[File:Propylbenzene_oxidations.png|frameless]]

这种对于某些键的选择性使其可用于分解例如[[煤|煤]]的复杂碳氢化合物混合物，以确定结构细节。<ref>{{cite journal|url = https://www.osti.gov/scitech/servlets/purl/5235716|title = Dihydroaromatic structure of Illinois No. 6 Monterey coal|first1 = Norman C.|last1 = Deno|first2 = Kenneth W.|last2 = Curry|first3 = Barbara A.|last3 = Greigger|first4 = A. Daniel|last4 = Jones|first5 = Walter G.|last5 = Rakitsky|first6 = Karen A.|last6 = Smith|first7 = Karen|last7 = Wagner|first8 = Robert D.|last8 = Minard|journal = Fuel|volume = 59|issue = 10|year = 1980|pages = 694–698|doi = 10.1016/0016-2361(80)90021-6|access-date = 2021-12-31|archive-date = 2020-06-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200626055756/https://www.osti.gov/biblio/5235716}}</ref><ref name=Deno1978/>

含有杂原子的芳香系统对这种开环反应有抵抗力，因为杂原子的氧化会优先发生，使三氟过氧乙酸的亲电攻击对芳香环失效。举个例子，[[嘌呤|嘌呤]]、[[吡啶|吡啶]]和[[喹啉|喹啉]]会先形成''N''-氧化物，<ref name = eEROS2012 />而像是八氟{{le|二苯并噻吩|dibenzothiophene}}的含硫杂环会被转化成砜。<ref name = FinOChem /><ref>{{cite journal|title = Polyfluoroaryl organometallic compounds. Part VIII. Synthesis of and nucleophilic substitution in octafluorodibenzofuran|first1 = R. D.|last1 = Chambers|first2 = J. A.|last2 = Cunningham|first3 = D. J.|last3 = Spring|journal = J. Chem. Soc. C|year = 1968|pages = 1560–1565|doi = 10.1039/J39680001560}}</ref>

含有[[苯环的亲电取代定位效应|活化基团]]的芳香环会被氧化成[[酚|酚]]，而不是发生开环反应。举个例子，[[均三甲苯|均三甲苯]]和三氟过氧乙酸反应的产物是{{le|均三甲苯酚|mesitol}}（2,4,6-三甲基苯酚）。<ref name = FinOChem />研究人员试图通过7-氧化脱乙酰氨基[[秋水仙素|秋水仙素]]的拜耳－维立格氧化反应合成内酯，虽然反应不成功，但实现了对芳香环氧化高产率生产酚的反应：<ref name = eEROS2012 /><ref>{{cite journal|title = Stereochemical variations on the colchicine motif. Peracid oxidation of thiocolchicone. Synthesis, conformation and inhibition of microtubule assembly|first1 = Ulf|last1 = Berg|first2 = Håkan|last2 = Bladha|first3 = Konstantinos|last3 = Mpamposa|journal = Org. Biomol. Chem.|year = 2004|volume = 2|issue = 14|pages = 2125–2130|doi = 10.1039/B402840F|pmid = 15254641}}</ref>

